Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.96,0:02:23.62,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,When you're having cake, shortcake tastes best.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.95,0:02:27.49,Default,Tango,0000,0000,0000,,But Agnes, yesterday you said cheesecake was the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.56,0:02:29.77,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow will be the tarts!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.23,0:02:31.89,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Tango should try one too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.04,0:02:34.10,Default,Tango,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.44,0:02:38.19,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Carina?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.48,0:02:40.66,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.99,0:02:43.47,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want my piece of cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.83,0:02:46.03,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't looking at her cake...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.23,0:02:47.79,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Then what were you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:49.83,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Leicester...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.24,0:02:54.09,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Please enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.29,0:02:55.21,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.68,0:02:57.46,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Leicester?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.58,0:02:58.18,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.60,0:03:04.07,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Is a talking automaton like Tango-san difficult to make?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:05.47,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Yes it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.99,0:03:08.99,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,To make Automata that can use its own heart and will to speak,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.30,0:03:11.91,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,you definitely need exceptional skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:13.26,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.67,0:03:17.48,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:21.39,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,No... it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.29,0:03:25.87,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,I still have my afternoon duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.04,0:03:27.71,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:30.07,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Best wishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.34,0:03:32.38,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks a lot, bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.99,0:03:35.98,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,She's always so busy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.21,0:03:37.98,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,But that's because she's the Archduke's daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.09,0:03:39.25,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,She's so reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.49,0:03:40.33,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.51,0:03:43.53,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Can you help me for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.74,0:03:54.31,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,I see. This is what Carina-sama is thinking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:57.22,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, is there anything we can help her with?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.53,0:03:59.08,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.37,0:04:00.39,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Just give me some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.92,0:04:06.34,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.62,0:04:08.30,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.76,0:04:10.73,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:13.78,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my... Where's Leicester and Annie-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.62,0:04:15.78,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Both of them are...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.01,0:04:17.53,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, that will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.59,0:04:18.42,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.72,0:04:20.32,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,But you sure are impressive...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.02,0:04:23.06,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to the Crystal monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.31,0:04:24.01,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.10,0:04:26.36,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Carina-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.79,0:04:28.04,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Carina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.67,0:04:32.17,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Leicester, Annie-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:34.96,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,W-What were the two of you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.45,0:04:37.29,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.31,0:04:38.11,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing important.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.44,0:04:44.13,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Carina-sama, there's a quest I'd like to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.37,0:04:52.84,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,This is a picture of the Laschuttato forest, and the Black-Rainbow flower which blooms inside it. {Spelling according to the map @06:37}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.13,0:04:55.01,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Black-Rainbow flower?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:04:57.75,Default,Nick,0000,0000,0000,,The rainbow is obvious, but why black?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.32,0:05:00.50,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,It used to be a black flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.99,0:05:04.89,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,It's said that it absorbs the surrounding light to make up the seven colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.58,0:05:07.41,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,That's unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.91,0:05:14.48,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. That means the surroundings of this flower are ominously dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.84,0:05:17.77,Default,Nick,0000,0000,0000,,I see. It's similar to Crystals absorbing Ale.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:19.80,Default,Nick,0000,0000,0000,,The flower is absorbing all the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.85,0:05:22.83,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,The forest is already very dark on its own...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.43,0:05:27.39,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,There's also the added risk of being attacked by Crystal monsters in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.28,0:05:30.78,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,It's a high level quest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.59,0:05:35.52,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,But it also means it's easier to find quality Crystals there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.94,0:05:41.34,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Besides, Oasis has strong members now, like Agnes and Chelsea-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.68,0:05:43.58,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,I feel we should be able to do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.42,0:05:45.74,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Carina-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.04,0:05:53.04,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. Let's accept this quest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.85,0:05:57.20,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's so amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.77,0:06:03.01,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,Minette-san, is this your first time taking a train?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.10,0:06:05.57,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's thrilling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:09.56,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, it's dangerous...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.31,0:06:11.60,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.73,0:06:14.63,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stick your body out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.75,0:06:15.59,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.01,0:06:19.40,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's good. There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.78,0:06:24.02,Default,Nick,0000,0000,0000,,They both look like close sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.90,0:06:25.78,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.35,0:06:28.68,Default,Nick,0000,0000,0000,,Say, about that Black-Rainbow flower...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:31.86,Default,Nick,0000,0000,0000,,The forest is vast, how do you plan to find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.65,0:06:33.97,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I have a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.89,0:06:39.05,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Carina-san, I suggest we scout from the sky first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.19,0:06:41.08,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:44.64,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Carina-sama can use her magic to fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.20,0:06:47.64,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.45,0:06:51.96,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Then, leave the sky search to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.11,0:06:54.82,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,We'll locate the encompassing dark points.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.88,0:06:59.38,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Agnes and the rest will retrieve the flowers at said points.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:03.79,Default,Nick,0000,0000,0000,,If the Crystal monsters appear, it'll be my turn to shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.58,0:07:07.81,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,How lucky.
