Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.41,0:07:11.39,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,We were at the train station because of a delivery quest...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:13.84,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,...and just so happened to meet Leicester and company.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.15,0:07:17.44,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I smell some sort of treasure coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.77,0:07:18.50,Default,Golem,0000,0000,0000,,Golem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.14,0:07:23.38,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry for fitting you into such a crammed cargo storage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:27.37,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,We should head to the passenger cabin now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.43,0:07:29.31,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, I'll go too.{added "Yep, " -masat}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.48,0:07:32.04,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I forgot to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:37.05,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,As it's a little too crammed, there's only one ticket to the passenger cabin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.13,0:07:40.18,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget such important details!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.18,0:07:43.46,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright. I'll give this to Nee-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:44.90,Default-Alt,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sign: Fresh goods
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.90,0:07:48.90,Default-Alt,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\pos(15.849057,20.25)}Sign Girl: Fresh goods
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.90,0:07:48.90,Default-Alt,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\pos(1895.09434,18)}Sign Golem: Fragile item
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.72,0:07:48.56,Default,Golem,0000,0000,0000,,Golem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:50.90,Default-Alt,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sign: Fresh goods
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.97,0:07:51.91,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I have to become cargo too!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.22,0:07:58.89,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, we'll be leaving first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.53,0:08:05.17,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's floating.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.82,0:08:10.81,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.31,0:08:17.82,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Carina-san, you're completely synced with Montecchia, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.50,0:08:22.72,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, because it's the staff you made for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:27.68,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Carina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:31.57,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,This is for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.14,0:08:34.82,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I made this for you.{I MADE THIS FOR YOU!! -masat}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.59,0:08:38.51,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:48.32,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to Montecchia that I'm able to roam the world despite my weak body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.70,0:08:51.79,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really glad to hear you say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.40,0:08:54.96,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, Leicester...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.78,0:08:56.37,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.86,0:09:00.41,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,What were you talking about with Annie-chan yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.47,0:09:01.95,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Carina-san, over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.86,0:09:07.50,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:09.68,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,That's probably the Black-Rainbow flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.26,0:09:11.29,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Let's contact everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.56,0:09:17.47,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, head north.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.05,0:09:19.58,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, north it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.80,0:09:27.10,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Once you see the river, keep going left.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.59,0:09:29.14,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,We got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.37,0:09:34.13,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,North should be this way, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.91,0:09:37.08,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,Using this grass as a landmark...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.49,0:09:40.83,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Continue walking straight along the cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.34,0:09:45.06,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Wow. Isn't this beautiful, Chel-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.55,0:09:47.32,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Chel-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:47.96,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.81,0:09:49.56,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?{added this -masat}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.16,0:09:51.51,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chel-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.87,0:09:56.23,Default,Chel,0000,0000,0000,,Left? Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.34,0:09:59.65,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Carina-sama! Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.85,0:10:01.62,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Look on the other side of the cliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.81,0:10:03.46,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Chel-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.13,0:10:08.11,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,You go ahead. I'll go fetch her and catch up later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.72,0:10:09.89,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.30,0:10:11.55,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stick with the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.82,0:10:14.29,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,Up ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.60,0:10:23.66,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,Leicester-san and company seem to be headed northward from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.88,0:10:27.49,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Golem, full speed ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.53,0:10:30.75,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,But, Nee-san..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:31.45,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:33.74,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,There's an endless swamp up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.64,0:10:38.66,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, tell me such important things earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.66,0:10:39.59,Default-Alt,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,You worked hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.19,0:10:57.70,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,This is incredible...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.92,0:11:01.66,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Leicester, be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.50,0:11:03.70,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:10.46,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the one?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.12,0:11:16.35,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Black-Rainbow flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.82,0:11:18.53,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,It's so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.73,0:11:29.75,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think the Crystal monsters would appear so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.51,0:11:31.47,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Leicester.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.81,0:11:33.57,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Stay close to me, Carina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.57,0:11:34.28,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:38.15,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,They are attacking us from the dark? So troublesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.87,0:11:41.19,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Let's use light magic to null the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.66,0:11:42.43,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:45.14,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,The light will be absorbed by the Black-Rainbow flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.79,0:11:46.97,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.63,0:11:51.71,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,On their next strike, I'll deflect the monster over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.65,0:11:55.18,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Then, use your magic on that area.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.04,0:11:57.13,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Can you do it, Carina-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.55,0:11:58.23,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.82,0:11:59.55,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.05,0:12:06.77,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Carina-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.97,0:12:13.96,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.97,0:12:16.98,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Where did the monster go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.86,0:12:27.52,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,You were too focused and didn't get good control over the strength of the magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:30.33,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.56,0:12:34.63,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.18,0:12:41.96,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Carina-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.93,0:12:50.25,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.34,0:12:54.19,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Leicester, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.90,0:12:56.91,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:03.87,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Leicester, please stop moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.54,0:13:07.79,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,We're caught in the vines.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.36,0:13:18.03,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.03,0:13:19.15,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Carina-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:20.05,Default,Nick,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.61,0:13:31.32,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look, Minette-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:34.95,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,You got the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.95,0:13:36.13,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,It's just... that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.46,0:13:40.04,Default,Nick,0000,0000,0000,,Hey?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.23,0:13:41.50,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Carina-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.84,0:13:52.29,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Finalizing confirmation, quest complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.29,0:13:53.60,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.69,0:13:55.84,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.99,0:13:59.20,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for giving everyone so much trouble today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.42,0:14:01.51,Default,Nick,0000,0000,0000,,You just need to be on your toes next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.14,0:14:03.98,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright, Carina-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.30,0:14:06.93,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I frightened everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.08,0:14:08.80,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,You're very unlucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.96,0:14:12.36,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Your magical powers were depleted at the last moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.77,0:14:14.19,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,What a disgrace...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.90,0:14:17.31,Default,Nick,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine since we completed the quest, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:21.74,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,We also got our hands on a rare Crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.18,0:14:24.29,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, on that matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:27.41,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Who should we give the Crystal to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.68,0:14:30.20,Default,Chelsea,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.88,0:14:32.00,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Agnes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.29,0:14:33.65,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.15,0:14:38.13,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Upgrading Montecchia with such a fine Crystal shouldn't be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.43,0:14:45.70,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking; if we used this Crystal, we might be able to install a talking functionality on Montecchia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:49.38,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Montecchia will be able to speak?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.83,0:14:52.76,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, Leicester and I were discussing about this yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:15:03.31,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,If Montecchia is able to talk, it'll be able to warn you of magic depletion like today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.95,0:15:06.74,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,It can also talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.10,0:15:08.98,Default,Minettes,0000,0000,0000,,That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.34,0:15:11.12,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Carina-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.29,0:15:16.67,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.73,0:15:47.53,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, I made some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.17,0:15:49.03,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.70,0:15:51.57,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right, Carina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:53.70,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Can you lend me a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:15:59.00,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,B-But I don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.90,0:16:02.36,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't Annie-chan be better?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:04.17,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.64,0:16:07.01,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,I heard from Agnes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.14,0:16:14.53,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,At least, you must have a good grade Crystal and professional skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:17.41,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,The most important thing are bonds, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.15,0:16:19.02,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Bonds?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.01,0:16:25.25,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Like Tango, he was a puppet I got for my birthday when I was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.38,0:16:30.62,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Items that are loved and respected will have a soul instilled in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.50,0:16:33.16,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,That's what my maitresse told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.38,0:16:36.06,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Bonds?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.54,0:16:42.52,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, those precious feelings you have for Montecchia are the most important ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:45.08,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:49.37,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Just exert magic into Montecchia like you always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.07,0:16:51.99,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,I'll control the direction of Ale flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.47,0:16:53.38,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.38,0:17:03.60,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:06.43,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's a pleasant smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.11,0:17:11.83,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. It's because I washed my hair in the bath just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.23,0:17:13.82,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.63,0:17:19.90,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Is it like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.46,0:17:22.89,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Logically, it shouldn't be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.72,0:17:25.20,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Carina-san, try activating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.97,0:17:26.97,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.64,0:17:32.29,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't seem to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.52,0:17:37.03,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that the Ale didn't flow successfully?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.85,0:17:39.77,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.65,0:17:43.68,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go and refill your tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:45.03,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.61,0:17:47.30,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Small things like this are fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.45,0:17:56.00,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.10,0:18:16.47,Insert Song,Song,0000,0000,0000,,In the buzzling town, we met by coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:23.77,Insert Song,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Why does this chanced encounter makes my heart beat so fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.97,0:18:31.49,Insert Song,Song,0000,0000,0000,,I finally understood that aimless without a goal is not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.70,0:18:31.58,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,If even this doesn't work...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.51,0:18:39.04,Insert Song,Song,0000,0000,0000,,The adventure around the world is in front of your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.85,0:18:32.70,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,It'll work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:36.45,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.38,0:18:43.24,Insert Song,Song,0000,0000,0000,,This is the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.24,0:18:46.96,Insert Song,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Entrusting diverse colors of dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.07,0:18:49.97,Insert Song,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Just like the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.97,0:18:54.20,Insert Song,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the transformation magic, where is that person?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.43,0:18:53.93,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:57.74,Insert Song,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Even though my voice is wavering.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.97,0:19:05.01,Insert Song,Song,0000,0000,0000,,I still firmly believe in the first step it takes to do miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.43,0:19:02.81,Default,Montecchia,0000,0000,0000,,Activation start.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.72,0:19:05.87,Default,Montecchia,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.21,0:19:10.36,Default,Montecchia,0000,0000,0000,,Did something surprise you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.89,0:19:13.17,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,We did it. It's a success, Carina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.33,0:19:16.37,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Montecchia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.12,0:19:18.37,Default,Mont,0000,0000,0000,,Situation understood. {grasped}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.86,0:19:23.96,Default,Mont,0000,0000,0000,,You're surprised that I'm able to speak and have a conscious will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:28.06,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, even though I expected it, it still took me by surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.08,0:19:31.24,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Montecchia, is there anything you're uncomfortable with?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.76,0:19:37.85,Default,Mont,0000,0000,0000,,Verifying status{status}; there is no problem with current condition, compared to the previous one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.40,0:19:39.37,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:47.54,Default,Mont,0000,0000,0000,,Delayed message: It has always been my will to serve my masters.
